## Overview
This document details all autoload and require statements that need to be updated
after moving files to correct namespaces.

## Main Entry Point: lib/uniword.rb

Current autoloads that need updating after file moves:

### Current Autoloads (in lib/uniword.rb)

```ruby
module Uniword
  # These will need to be removed or updated:
  autoload :NumberingConfiguration, 'uniword/numbering_configuration'
  autoload :NumberingDefinition, 'uniword/numbering_definition'
  autoload :NumberingInstance, 'uniword/numbering_instance'
  autoload :NumberingLevel, 'uniword/numbering_level'
  autoload :StylesConfiguration, 'uniword/styles_configuration'
  autoload :ColorScheme, 'uniword/color_scheme'
  autoload :FontScheme, 'uniword/font_scheme'
  autoload :FormatScheme, 'uniword/format_scheme'
end
```

### After Move to Wordprocessingml Namespace

```ruby
module Uniword
  module Wordprocessingml
    autoload :NumberingConfiguration, 'uniword/wordprocessingml/numbering_configuration'
    autoload :NumberingDefinition, 'uniword/wordprocessingml/numbering_definition'
    autoload :NumberingInstance, 'uniword/wordprocessingml/numbering_instance'
    autoload :NumberingLevel, 'uniword/wordprocessingml/numbering_level'
    autoload :StylesConfiguration, 'uniword/wordprocessingml/styles_configuration'
  end
end
```

### After Move to Drawingml Namespace

```ruby
