## Backwards Compatibility Aliases

To maintain backwards compatibility for existing code, add aliases in lib/uniword.rb:

```ruby
module Uniword
  # Backwards compatibility aliases
  NumberingConfiguration = Wordprocessingml::NumberingConfiguration
  NumberingDefinition = Wordprocessingml::NumberingDefinition
  NumberingInstance = Wordprocessingml::NumberingInstance
  NumberingLevel = Wordprocessingml::NumberingLevel
  StylesConfiguration = Wordprocessingml::StylesConfiguration

  # Theme-related aliases (already exist)
  Theme = Drawingml::Theme
  ColorScheme = Drawingml::ColorScheme
  FontScheme = Drawingml::FontScheme
  FormatScheme = Drawingml::FormatScheme
end
```

