## Module Declaration Changes

When moving files, update the module declarations:

### Before (in lib/uniword/numbering_level.rb)

```ruby
module Uniword
  class NumberingLevel < Lutaml::Model::Serializable
    # ...
  end
end
```

### After (in lib/uniword/wordprocessingml/numbering_level.rb)

```ruby
module Uniword
  module Wordprocessingml
    class NumberingLevel < Lutaml::Model::Serializable
      # ...
    end
  end
end
```

## Namespace References in XML Mappings

Update XML namespace references in moved classes:

```ruby
# Ensure correct namespace constant is used
xml do
  element 'lvl'
  namespace Uniword::Ooxml::Namespaces::WordProcessingML  # Use correct constant
end
```

## Require Relative Updates

If files use `require_relative`, update paths:

### Before (in lib/uniword/numbering_configuration.rb)

```ruby
require_relative 'numbering_definition'
require_relative 'numbering_instance'
```

### After (in lib/uniword/wordprocessingml/numbering_configuration.rb)

```ruby
require_relative 'numbering_definition'
require_relative 'numbering_instance'
# OR use full path:
require_relative '../numbering_definition'  # if still needed
```

